%md
# PERFILAMIENTO DE POTENCIALES CONTRIBUYENTES DEL IMPUESTO A LA RENTA
PROBLEMA
Existen personas naturales generadoras de renta que actualmente no cuentan con un registro en RUC por lo que consiguen evadir el pago de tributos.

OBJETIVO
Perfilar y segmentar a los potenciales contribuyentes generadores de renta y que actualmente no se encuentren tributando.

PROCEDIMIENTO REALIZADO

Para poder identificar a los potenciales contribuyentes generadores de renta se exploró las tablas vfp_20190213 (Vector Fiscal) y mod_fic_reniec_20190213 (Reniec)  de la base de datos db_tributario.

De esta manera se excluye a las personas jurídicas.

%livy2.sql
create table ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.tt_itf_2018_nosunat as 
select a.periodo_operacion,	a.cod_operacion,	a.modal_operacion,	a.tipo_movimiento,	a.tipo_dcto_declado,	trim(a.n_dcto_declado) as n_dcto_declado,	a.cic_declado,	
a.nota_abono,	a.formulario,	a.n_orden,	a.tipo_operacion,	a.periodo_rev,	a.tipo_dcto_declate,	a.n_dcto_declate,	a.cic_declate,	
a.mto_base,	a.mto_impuesto,	a.fecha_presentacion,	a.cod_paisop,	a.cod_paisce,	b.vfp_numruc,	b.vfp_dni,	b.num_docide_pnat,	b.fec_nac_pnat,	b.des_estciv_pnat,	b.des_sexo_pnat,	b.edad_20190214,	b.cod_ubigeo_pnat,	b.departamento,	b.provincia,	b.distrito,	b.des_domici_pnat,	b.num_doc_ide_id,	b.num_docsoc
from db_tributario.itf_2018 a
inner join ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.tt_reniec_sinruc10plamerlsolcios b
on trim(a.n_dcto_declado) = b.num_docide_pnat

paragraphs.text:
%livy2.sql
create table ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.tt_itf_2018_nosunat_resumen stored as parquet as 
SELECT  n_dcto_declado,
round(sum(case when cod_operacion in ('03','12','13') then if(mto_base is null,mto_impuesto/0.00005,mto_base) else 0 end),0) ingreso,
round(sum(if(mto_base is null,mto_impuesto/0.00005,mto_base))- sum(case when cod_operacion in ('03','12','13') then if(mto_base is null,mto_impuesto/0.00005,mto_base) else 0 end),0) egresos,
round(sum(if(mto_base is null,mto_impuesto/0.00005,mto_base)),0) total,
count(*) as transacciones
FROM ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.tt_itf_2018_nosunat a
group  by n_dcto_declado

paragraphs.text:
%md
Se inicio el analisis realizando un filtro que nos permita excluir a aquellas personas que presentaran RUC en la tabla t4241cabcpe_v1 (que guarda información de los comprobantes de pago electronicos)de la base de datos "ecommerce, creandose así una tabla llamada "cpe_pn" en la base de datos "ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes" con loa registros de las personas que no cuentan con RUC.

%livy2.sql
create table ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.cpe_pn as
select *
from (select length(trim(num_docide_recep)) as len, a.*
from ecommerce.t4241cabcpe_v1 a)
where len = 8

%md
Dicha tabla descrita anteriormente, cuenta con un total de 122,207,866 registros

%md
Posteriormente, se procedio a unir las tablas "cpe_pn" y "tt_reniec_sinruc10plamerlsolcios" por medio de los dni registrados en ambas tablas de tal manera que nos quedemos con la información de las compras realizadas por cada individuo que no se encuentra en el vector fiscal, no esta registrado en el plame, ni figura como socio o representante legal.

%livy2.sql
create table ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.cpe_pn_reniec_sinsunat as
select *
from ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.cpe_pn a
inner join ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.tt_reniec_sinruc10plamerlsolcios b
on trim(a.num_docide_recep) = b.num_docide_pnat
--group by cod_docide_recep order by 2 desc

%md
Con el fin de obtener los montos reales de igv, de venta, y de importe total se realizo un cálculo de los montos respectivos de acuerdo al tipo de comprobante de pago, donde se sumaron las facturas, boletas de venta, notas de debito y se sustrajo las notas de credito de cada individuo para el año 2018.
Dicha información se guardo en la tabla "cpe_pn_reniec_sinsunat_resumen" de la base de datos "ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes".

select categoria_imp_total_real, count(*) as personas,sum(mto_importe_total_real) as suma_imp_tot_real
from (select case when mto_importe_total_real<=0 then '0' 
                  when mto_importe_total_real>0 and mto_importe_total_real<=30000 then '<0-30 000]' 
                  when mto_importe_total_real>30000 and mto_importe_total_real<=200000 then '<30 000-200 000]' 
                  when mto_importe_total_real>200000 and mto_importe_total_real<=1000000 then '<200 000-1 000 000]' 
                  when mto_importe_total_real>1000000 and mto_importe_total_real<=10000000 then '<1 000 000-10 000 000]' else '<10 000 000-Inf' end as categoria_imp_total_real,a.* 
from ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.cpe_pn_reniec_sinsunat_resumen a)
group by categoria_imp_total_real

%livy2.sql
create table ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.cpe_pn_reniec_sinsunat_resumen as
select a.*, mto_importe_total_factura + mto_importe_total_boleta + mto_importe_total_nota_debito - mto_importe_total_nota_credito as mto_importe_total_real, 
mto_total_venta_factura+mto_total_venta_boleta+mto_total_venta_nota_debito-mto_total_venta_nota_credito as mto_total_venta_real,
mto_total_igv_factura+mto_total_igv_boleta+mto_total_igv_nota_debito-mto_total_igv_nota_credito as mto_total_igv_real

from (
select  num_docide_recep, count(distinct num_docide_recep), count(*) as cpe, sum(mto_importe_total) as mto_importe_total, 

sum(mto_importe_total * case when cod_cpe in("01")  then 1 else 0 end) as mto_importe_total_factura,
sum(mto_importe_total * case when cod_cpe in("03")  then 1 else 0 end) as mto_importe_total_boleta,
sum(mto_importe_total * case when cod_cpe in("08")  then 1 else 0 end) as mto_importe_total_nota_debito,
sum(mto_importe_total * case when cod_cpe in("07") then 1 else 0 end) as mto_importe_total_nota_credito, 
sum(mto_importe_total * case when cod_cpe not in ("01","03","08","07") then 1 else 0 end) as mto_importe_total_otroscpe,

sum(mto_total_venta * case when cod_cpe in("01")  then 1 else 0 end) as mto_total_venta_factura,
sum(mto_total_venta * case when cod_cpe in("03")  then 1 else 0 end) as mto_total_venta_boleta,
sum(mto_total_venta * case when cod_cpe in("08")  then 1 else 0 end) as mto_total_venta_nota_debito,
sum(mto_total_venta * case when cod_cpe in("07") then 1 else 0 end) as mto_total_venta_nota_credito, 
sum(mto_total_venta * case when cod_cpe not in ("01","03","08","07") then 1 else 0 end) as mto_total_venta_otroscpe,

sum(mto_total_igv * case when cod_cpe in("01")  then 1 else 0 end) as mto_total_igv_factura,
sum(mto_total_igv * case when cod_cpe in("03")  then 1 else 0 end) as mto_total_igv_boleta,
sum(mto_total_igv * case when cod_cpe in("08")  then 1 else 0 end) as mto_total_igv_nota_debito,
sum(mto_total_igv * case when cod_cpe in ("07") then 1 else 0 end) as mto_total_igv_nota_credito, 
sum(mto_total_igv * case when cod_cpe not in ("01","03","08","07") then 1 else 0 end) as mto_total_igv_otroscpe

from ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.cpe_pn_reniec_sinsunat
where substring(fec_emision,1,4)="2018" and trim(cod_docide_recep) in ("1","01")
group by num_docide_recep
order by sum(mto_importe_total) desc) a

create table ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.tt_ben as
select doc_ben, count(distinct doc_eje) as ben_eje, count(distinct doc_ord) as ben_ord from 
(
select b.*,
case when regexp_replace(nvl(num_doceje,""),"[^0-9]","")!='' then num_doceje else num_ruceje end as doc_eje, 
case when regexp_replace(nvl(num_docord,""),"[^0-9]","")!='' then num_docord else num_rucord end as doc_ord, 
case when regexp_replace(nvl(num_docben,""),"[^0-9]","")!='' then num_docben else num_rucben end as doc_ben 
from db_externo.t9017repopefin_2018_cleanv1 b) a
group by doc_ben

%livy2.sql
create table ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.tt_ord as
select doc_ord, count(distinct doc_ben) as ord_ben, count(distinct doc_eje) as ord_eje from 
(
select b.*,
case when regexp_replace(nvl(num_doceje,""),"[^0-9]","")!='' then num_doceje else num_ruceje end as doc_eje, 
case when regexp_replace(nvl(num_docord,""),"[^0-9]","")!='' then num_docord else num_rucord end as doc_ord, 
case when regexp_replace(nvl(num_docben,""),"[^0-9]","")!='' then num_docben else num_rucben end as doc_ben 
from db_externo.t9017repopefin_2018_cleanv1 b) a
group by doc_ord

%livy2.sql
create table ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.tt_eje as
select doc_eje, count(distinct doc_ben) as eje_ben, count(distinct doc_ord) as eje_ord from 
(
select b.*,
case when regexp_replace(nvl(num_doceje,""),"[^0-9]","")!='' then num_doceje else num_ruceje end as doc_eje, 
case when regexp_replace(nvl(num_docord,""),"[^0-9]","")!='' then num_docord else num_rucord end as doc_ord, 
case when regexp_replace(nvl(num_docben,""),"[^0-9]","")!='' then num_docben else num_rucben end as doc_ben 
from db_externo.t9017repopefin_2018_cleanv1 b) a
group by doc_eje

%livy2.sql

inner join ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.tt_ord b on a.doc_ben=b.doc_ord
inner join ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.tt_eje c on b.doc_ord=c.doc_eje

%livy2.sql
create table ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.tt_migraciones1618 as
select nrodoc as nro_doc, sum(case when tipoviaje = 'S' then 1 else 0 end) as mig_salida_peru,sum(case when tipoviaje = 'E' then 1 else 0 end) as mig_entrada_pais, count(*) as mig_registos,
    sum(case when destinoprocedencia in ('ARG','BOL','BRA','CHL','COL','ECU','PER','PRY','URY','VEN') and tipoviaje = 'S' then 1 else 0 end)/sum(case when tipoviaje = 'S' then 1 else 0 end) as mig_porc_salidas_americas,
    max(cast(to_date(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(fechaviaje, 'yyyy-MM-dd'))) as date)) as mig_ultima_fecha,
    min(cast(to_date(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(fechaviaje, 'yyyy-MM-dd'))) as date)) as mig_primera_fecha,
    floor(datediff(max(cast(to_date(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(fechaviaje, 'yyyy-MM-dd'))) as date)),min(cast(to_date(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(fechaviaje, 'yyyy-MM-dd'))) as date)))) as mig_diferencia_dias,
    floor(datediff(max(cast(to_date(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(fechaviaje, 'yyyy-MM-dd'))) as date)),min(cast(to_date(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(fechaviaje, 'yyyy-MM-dd'))) as date))))/sum(case when tipoviaje = 'S' then 1 else 0 end) as mig_prom_dias_viaje
from db_externo.mod_migraciones_2016_2018_dni
group by nrodoc

create table ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.md_potenciales_contribuyentes as 
select a.nro_doc,fec_nac_pnat,des_estciv_pnat,des_sexo_pnat,edad_20190214 as edad,cod_ubigeo_pnat,departamento,provincia,distrito,des_domici_pnat,itf_ingreso,itf_egresos,itf_total,itf_transacciones,pre_predios,pre_mto_autov,pre_area_const,pred_area_comun,cpe_comprobantes_electronico,cpe_mto_total_venta_real,cpe_mto_total_igv_real,cpe_mto_total_venta_otroscpe,cpe_mto_total_igv_otroscpe,rcc_prom_normal_6m,rcc_prom_cpp_6m,rcc_prom_dudoso_6m,rcc_prom_perdida_6m,rcc_prom_ent,rcc_num_entrep_dic2018,rcc_score_cal_dic2018,rosf_ord_ben,rosf_ord_eje,rosf_ben_eje,rosf_ben_ord,rosf_eje_ord,rosf_eje_ben,mig_salida_peru,mig_entrada_pais,mig_registos,mig_porc_salidas_americas,mig_ultima_fecha,mig_primera_fecha,mig_diferencia_dias,mig_prom_dias_viaje
from (select trim(num_docide_pnat) as nro_doc,fec_nac_pnat,des_estciv_pnat,des_sexo_pnat,edad_20190214,cod_ubigeo_pnat,departamento,provincia,distrito,des_domici_pnat from ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.tt_reniec_sinruc10plamerlsolcios) a
left join (select trim(n_dcto_declado) as nro_doc,ingreso as itf_ingreso,egresos as itf_egresos,total as itf_total,transacciones as itf_transacciones from ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.tt_itf_2018_nosunat_resumen) b on a.nro_doc = b.nro_doc
left join (select trim(nro_doc) as nro_doc,predios as pre_predios,mto_autov as pre_mto_autov,area_const as pre_area_const,area_comun as pred_area_comun from ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.tt_muni_predios_reniec_sinsunat) c on a.nro_doc = c.nro_doc
left join (select trim(num_docide_recep) as nro_doc, cpe as cpe_comprobantes_electronico, mto_total_venta_real as cpe_mto_total_venta_real,mto_total_igv_real as cpe_mto_total_igv_real,mto_total_venta_otroscpe as cpe_mto_total_venta_otroscpe,mto_total_igv_otroscpe as cpe_mto_total_igv_otroscpe from ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.cpe_pn_reniec_sinsunat_resumen) d on a.nro_doc = d.nro_doc
left join (select trim(num_docide_pnat) as nro_doc,prom_normal_6m as rcc_prom_normal_6m, prom_cpp_6m as rcc_prom_cpp_6m, prom_dudoso_6m as rcc_prom_dudoso_6m, prom_perdida_6m as rcc_prom_perdida_6m, prom_ent as rcc_prom_ent, num_entrep_dic2018 as rcc_num_entrep_dic2018, score_cal_dic2018 as rcc_score_cal_dic2018 from ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.indicadores_comportamiento_rcc_sinsunat) e on a.nro_doc = e.nro_doc
left join ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.rosf_reniec f on a.nro_doc = f.nro_doc
left join ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.tt_migraciones1618 g on a.nro_doc = g.nro_doc

create table ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.md_potenciales_contribuyentes_positivos as 
select v1+v2+v3+v4+v5+v6 as nro_columnas, b.*,c.*
from (select nvl(itf_total,0) + nvl(pre_mto_autov,0) + nvl(cpe_mto_total_venta_real,0) as total,
	  case when itf_total is null then 0 else 1 end as v1,
	  case when pre_mto_autov is null then 0 else 1 end as v2,
	  case when cpe_mto_total_venta_real is null then 0 else 1 end as v3,
	  case when rcc_num_entrep_dic2018 is null then 0 else 1 end as v4,
	  case when rosf_ord_eje is null then 0 else 1 end as v5,
	  case when mig_salida_peru is null then 0 else 1 end as v6,
	  a.*
	  from ds12_potenciales_contribuyentes.md_potenciales_contribuyentes a
	 ) b
inner join (select num_docide_pnat,des_apepat_pnat,des_apemat_pnat,des_nombre_pnat from db_tributario.mod_fic_reniec_20190213) c 
on b.nro_doc = trim(c.num_docide_pnat)
where v1+v2+v3+v4+v5+v6>0
